I just bought a 10k worth of security through an online broker and my friend wants to sell it through a different broker . Is it possible ?

Multi-choice problem : Which is NOT true about the above ?

 (1). You are not able to do that .;
 (2). You can do that .;
 (3). You can sell a 10k security through a different broker .;
 (4). You are not able to do that .;

I think the answer is

(4).

